Name: DigitalFingerprintValue
Description: Contains the value of the specified digital fingerprint.

Name: AlgorithmSpecification
Description: Specifies the type of the fingerprint (what algorithm or scheme).

Name: AlgorithmVersion
Description: Contains the version of the algorithm.

Name: Type
Description: Brief identification of the type of data fingerprint used. The data fingerprint may be for the data file (storage format specific) or data (format neutral).
